name: Jupitee
overview:
With Jupitee you can have your own mobile app in a few easy steps, with no programming involved, but with plenty of features and give your customers an app they will love to use.

Jupitee offers an intuitive, automated system to build apps and have them posted to the app store in as little as a day. It is like Wordpress for mobile apps. The core is the content management system (CMS) where you manage your app’s look and feel and fill it with content. It is entirely do-it-yourself with no need for coding.

The platform lets you do some pretty cool things – you can allow users to see your company presentation, your photos, get event dates, stream your videos from YouTube, locate you on the map, contact you with a single click and other such stuff. You also have your own custom categories to present your content in any structure you like. There’s even a fan-wall where your app users can interact with each other. And everything can be updated online – you can add new videos, pics, news, etc. quickly and easily, and it will automatically push out and update the app on all their iPhones.
